{"word":"ἐναγωνίζομαι","slug":"ἐναγωνίζομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐναγωνίζομαι</b></el> <el>(ionic <a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-ιεῦμαι</el>) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a> <i>to contend</i> or <i>fight among</i> others, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:dative'>dat.</a>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><el>γῆ εὐμενὴς ἐναγωνίζεσθαι</el> favourable <i>to fight in</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}